# EduTrack System 🎓

A Java-based Student Learning Management System with GUI.

## Features
- Login System
- Add Student
- Delete Student
- Add Course
- View Students
- View Courses
- View Enrollments
- Save Data to File

## Technologies Used
- Java
- Swing (GUI)

## How to Run
1. Open project in IntelliJ
2. Run Main.java or LoginGUI.java

